    "hash": "wfbFa7W3ZDPU0/YwP5RRMm2zLvo=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:47.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# User Manifest Feed Structure\n\nThe user manifest feed lives at topic `ph:v2:user:<address>` and is owned by the user's signer address. Each feed index points to a `/bytes` upload containing encrypted JSON.\n\n## Schema\n\n```json\n{\n  \"address\": \"0xAlice\",\n  \"drives\": {\n    \"drive-abc\": {\n      \"name\": \"Finance Drive\",\n      \"documentIds\": [],\n      \"lastUpdated\": \"2026-04-10T12:00:00Z\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"stamps\": {},\n  \"documents\": {},\n  \"updatedAt\": \"2026-04-10T12:00:00Z\"\n}\n```\n\n## Role\n\n- Serves as the top-level index into a user's data on Swarm\n- Points to drives (each with its own manifest feed)\n- Tracks postage stamps and standalone documents\n- Recovery starts here: read the user manifest, then descend into drive manifests, then document manifests\n",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:47.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:47.000Z"
    }
  },
